<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>About HouseIn</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #F2F0EF; /* Light background color */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 30px 55px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px #351E10; /* Box shadow */
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px); /* Slight hover effect */
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 35px;
            color: #351E10;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #351E10;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #351E10;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 15px; /* Reduce overall padding for smaller screens */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to HouseIn</h2>
            <p>Welcome to HouseIn, your trusted partner in building your dream home. HouseIn is an interactive web application that serves as a communication interface between clients and constructors, simplifying the process of finding skilled professionals for your construction needs.</p>

            <p>We understand that local workers often face challenges in finding opportunities due to high competition. That’s why our platform is dedicated to providing significant opportunities for these workers by connecting them with available jobs in carpentry, plumbing, electrical work, and more.</p>

            <p>By leveraging advanced machine learning tools, HouseIn not only predicts home prices but also recommends the best professionals based on comprehensive client reviews and ratings. Our user-friendly interface reduces the time spent searching for construction services and job opportunities, ensuring that both clients and local workers can focus on what truly matters.</p>

            <p>Whether you’re starting from scratch or renovating, our goal is to simplify your home-building journey while keeping you within budget. With HouseIn, you can confidently embark on your project, knowing that skilled professionals with a proven track record of excellence are just a click away.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
